---
// 首页入口文件
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <title>HUAT FSAC</title>
    <meta name="description" content="学生工程师的冠军梦工厂。" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.png" />
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        background: #030303;
        color: #f5f7fb;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        padding: 2rem;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: #f39c12;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        opacity: 0.8;
      }
      .buttons {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      a:hover {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      }
      a.primary {
        background: #f39c12;
        border-color: #f39c12;
        color: #151515;
      }
      a.primary:hover {
        background: #e67e22;
      }
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        h1 {
          font-size: 2rem;
        }
        p {
          font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .buttons {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: center;
        }
        a {
          width: 200px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>HUAT FSAC</h1>
      <p>学生工程师的冠军梦工厂</p>
      <div class="buttons">
        <a class="primary" href="/docs-center/">文档中心</a>
        <a href="/archive/2024/2024-learning-roadmap/">学习路线</a>
        <a href="/team/">关于我们</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>